---
import { contactConfig } from '../../config/contact';
---
<header class="hero" id="top">
  <div class="container hero-grid">
    <div class="reveal">
      <span class="pill">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 3l1.9 5.1L19 10l-5.1 1.9L12 17l-1.9-5.1L5 10l5.1-1.9L12 3z" fill="currentColor"/></svg>
        Credenciada no INPI
      </span>
      <h1>Sua marca protegida com <span class="g-cyan">transparência e</span> <span class="g-purple">tecnologia.</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Registramos e protegemos sua marca no INPI com pesquisa por inteligência artificial, acompanhamento diário e um pagamento único — sem pegadinhas.</p>
      <div class="hero-ctas">
        <a class="button button--secondary" href="#planos">Ver planos
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a class="button button--dark" href="#duvidas">Tirar dúvidas</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-divider"></div>
      <div class="hero-stats">
        <div><div class="s-num">48h</div><div class="s-lbl">para protocolo</div></div>
        <div><div class="s-num">10 anos</div><div class="s-lbl">de validade</div></div>
        <div><div class="s-num">100%</div><div class="s-lbl">transparência</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-visual reveal">
      <form class="hero-form" id="heroLeadForm" data-whatsapp-number={contactConfig.whatsappNumber} novalidate>
        <span id="cadastro" class="hero-form-anchor" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <img class="hero-form-mark" src="/images/logo-mark.png" alt="" aria-hidden="true" />
        <p class="hero-form-eyebrow">Consulta rápida</p>
        <h2>Vamos registrar sua marca?</h2>
        <div class="hero-form-grid">
          <div class="field"><label for="h-nome">Nome completo</label><input id="h-nome" name="nome" type="text" placeholder="Seu nome" required /></div>
          <div class="field"><label for="h-whats">WhatsApp</label><input id="h-whats" name="whats" type="tel" placeholder="(00) 00000-0000" required /></div>
          <div class="field"><label for="h-marca">Nome da marca</label><input id="h-marca" name="marca" type="text" placeholder="Como se chama sua marca" required /></div>
          <div class="field"><label for="h-cnpj">CNPJ (se tiver)</label><input id="h-cnpj" name="cnpj" type="text" placeholder="00.000.000/0000-00" /></div>
          <div class="field full"><label for="h-area">Área de atuação</label><input id="h-area" name="area" type="text" placeholder="Ex: moda, alimentação, tecnologia..." required /></div>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="button button--secondary">
          Quero registrar minha marca
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </button>
        <p class="hero-form-note">Sem compromisso. Você fala direto com a Registrium pelo WhatsApp.</p>
        <div class="hero-form-ok" id="heroLeadOk">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M4 12l5 5L20 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
          Abrindo o WhatsApp com seus dados…
        </div>
      </form>
      <div class="hero-form-badge">
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M4 12l5 5L20 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        +20 marcas já registradas no INPI
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>
<script>
  const heroForm = document.getElementById('heroLeadForm') as HTMLFormElement | null;
  if (heroForm) {
    const whatsappNumber = heroForm.dataset.whatsappNumber;
    heroForm.addEventListener('submit', (event) => {
      event.preventDefault();
      if (!heroForm.checkValidity()) {
        heroForm.reportValidity();
        return;
      }
      const data = Object.fromEntries(new FormData(heroForm).entries());
      let message = 'Olá! Quero registrar minha marca com a Registrium.\n\n';
      message += `Nome: ${data.nome}\nMarca: ${data.marca}\nWhatsApp: ${data.whats}\nÁrea de atuação: ${data.area}`;
      if (data.cnpj) message += `\nCNPJ: ${data.cnpj}`;
      document.getElementById('heroLeadOk')?.classList.add('show');
      window.open(`https://wa.me/${whatsappNumber}?text=${encodeURIComponent(message)}`, '_blank', 'noopener');
    });
  }
</script>
<style>
.hero { position: relative; overflow: hidden; background:
    radial-gradient(120% 90% at 85% 40%, rgba(70,110,230,.28), transparent 55%),
    radial-gradient(90% 80% at 15% 10%, rgba(120,70,200,.22), transparent 60%),
    linear-gradient(125deg, var(--color-navy-950) 0%, var(--color-indigo-900) 55%, var(--color-purple-900) 100%); }
.hero-grid { position: relative; z-index: 1; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.08fr .92fr; gap: 3rem; align-items: center; padding: 6rem 0 5.25rem; }
.pill { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: .55rem; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.22); background: rgba(255,255,255,.06); color: var(--color-white); border-radius: 999px; padding: .55rem 1.05rem; font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; font-size: .75rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .13em; text-transform: uppercase; }
.pill svg { width: .95rem; height: .95rem; color: #8fd0f5; }
.hero h1 { color: var(--color-white); font-weight: 800; font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 6vw, 4.6rem); line-height: 1.02; margin-top: 1.6rem; }
.hero h1 .g-cyan { background: var(--grad-cyan); -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; color: transparent; }
.hero h1 .g-purple { background: var(--grad-purple); -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; color: transparent; }
.hero-sub { color: var(--color-on-dark); font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 31rem; margin-top: 1.6rem; }
.hero-ctas { display: flex; gap: .875rem; margin-top: 2.1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.hero-divider { height: 1px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.12); margin-top: 3.25rem; max-width: 38rem; }
.hero-stats { display: flex; gap: 3.5rem; margin-top: 1.6rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.hero-stats .s-num { font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 2.1rem; color: var(--color-white); line-height: 1; }
.hero-stats .s-lbl { font-size: .84rem; color: var(--color-on-dark-soft); margin-top: .5rem; }
.hero-visual { position: relative; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
.hero-visual::before { content: ""; position: absolute; width: 80%; aspect-ratio: 1; border-radius: 50%; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(90,120,240,.45), transparent 68%); filter: blur(34px); }

.hero-form { position: relative; width: 100%; max-width: 27rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,.97); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 2rem 1.875rem 1.75rem; box-shadow: 0 40px 80px -30px rgba(6,8,30,.55); }
.hero-form-mark { position: absolute; top: -1.4rem; right: 1.5rem; width: 3rem; filter: drop-shadow(0 10px 20px rgba(60,40,150,.4)); animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite; }
.hero-form-eyebrow { margin: 0 0 .3rem; font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: .75rem; letter-spacing: .12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-violet); }
.hero-form h2 { font-size: 1.375rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.2; }
.hero-form-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: .875rem; margin-bottom: .875rem; }
.hero-form .field { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .4rem; }
.hero-form .field.full { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
.hero-form .field label { font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; font-size: .75rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-text); }
.hero-form .field input { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: .9rem; color: var(--color-text); background: var(--color-white); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: .65rem; padding: .7rem .85rem; outline: none; transition: border-color .15s ease; width: 100%; }
.hero-form .field input:focus { border-color: var(--color-blue); }
.hero-form .button { width: 100%; margin-top: .4rem; }
.hero-form-note { font-size: .72rem; color: var(--color-muted); text-align: center; margin: .75rem 0 0; }
.hero-form-ok { display: none; align-items: center; gap: .5rem; background: #eaf6ef; border: 1px solid #bee3cb; color: #1f7a4d; border-radius: .65rem; padding: .6rem .8rem; font-size: .78rem; font-weight: 600; margin-top: .75rem; }
.hero-form-ok.show { display: flex; }
.hero-form-badge { position: absolute; left: 1.5rem; bottom: -1.1rem; z-index: 2; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: .5rem; background: #eaf6ef; border: 1px solid #bee3cb; color: #1f7a4d; border-radius: 999px; padding: .55rem 1rem; font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; font-size: .75rem; font-weight: 700; box-shadow: 0 14px 28px -14px rgba(6,8,30,.5); animation: badgeFloat 5s ease-in-out infinite; }
.hero-form-badge svg { flex: none; color: #1f7a4d; }
@keyframes float { 0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); } 50% { transform: translateY(-10px); } }
@keyframes badgeFloat { 0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); } 50% { transform: translateY(-6px); } }
@media (max-width: 920px) { .hero-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.25rem; padding: 4rem 0 4.25rem; } .hero-visual { order: -1; max-width: 27rem; margin: 0 auto; padding-bottom: 1.5rem; } }
@media (max-width: 560px) { .hero-ctas { flex-direction: column; } .hero-ctas .button { width: 100%; } .hero-stats { gap: 1.875rem; } .hero-form { padding: 1.75rem 1.375rem 1.5rem; } .hero-form-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .hero-form-badge { font-size: .68rem; padding: .5rem .8rem; left: 1.1rem; } }
</style>
